1.0.name: wordpress/austin-tech-events-calendar
1.0.description:
Want to promote the tech community in Austin? This is your Wordpress plugin! You can see an example of this plugin on my blog's sidebar.

The Austin Tech Events Calendar plugin is a branch of wpng-calendar, a Wordpress plugin for integrating a Google calendar into your WordPress blog. It is customized to best display events from the door64.com events calendar.

For more information about this plugin checkout Dusty's blog post about this plugin. And check out the documentation from the original wpng-calendar site.
